      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_011_000079",
    "sentence": "丁巳，皇太太后傅氏崩。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_011_000080",
    "sentence": "三月，丞相嘉有罪，下獄死。",
